{"tid":2323683,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「解迷思」點解我地需要杜汶澤 我地要撐佢既喱騷平台","createTime":"2020-12-13T10:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T12:32:18.000Z","uid":268373,"like":114,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"9303ee9827a1bad18653a105110937b097c62ee9","tid":2323683,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">過去一年喇，唔知大家罷藍店既時候會否有少少吃力感，無力感呢？</span><br />\n：屌，呢間藍架？咁叫食呢間囉<br />\n：喂，呢條友藍嫁喎 睇第二個人啦<br />\n：點解上大銀幕既都係藍屍黎既？<br />\n<span class=\"large\">相信大家初頭都一定遇過咁既情況 <br />\n原因好簡單 <span class=\"blue\">因為香港一早比藍紅資財團壟斷，一街都係藍連鎖店 （大家樂 美心 怡和 TVB 中信 甚至Facebook Ig Youtube都有打壓  呢個世界被財團壟斷 我地用到既服務 得到既資訊全部都會受呢啲財團、企業家既操作 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">結論：我地需要黃色資本家 我地要有有權力既財團、企業</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/okUwhjH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FokUwhjH.png&h=99941e6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">喱騷就係一間擴展緊既黃色企業 </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjTH8r8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjTH8r8.png&h=4a637f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F7oH8r9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF7oH8r9.png&h=e2ec81ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddUL6dQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddUL6dQ.png&h=f67c7b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">大家都見到 好簡單一句 <span class=\"orange\">誰是老闆？</span>杜汶澤理念好直接 要創造一個唔再比中資藍資老闆控制既娛樂平台 真真正正既<span class=\"gold\">黃色企業</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">要擺脫藍紅資企業壟斷局面 我地就要成立屬於我地既黃資企業 壯大、對抗、消滅佢地 而壯大呢一步 其實已經做緊</span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">快餐代表：齊柏林熱狗店 全港有29間分店</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"large\">齊柏林係好典型新興既<span class=\"orange\">連鎖黃店</span>我就係要呢啲.jpg 我就係要有能力同紅藍資本抗衡既黃店 </span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zp7UZCp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzp7UZCp.png&h=26aebfa2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ryx9OvK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fryx9OvK.png&h=f7dd0718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">茶餐廳代表 瓏門冰室 光榮冰室 分店遍佈港九</span><br />\n<span class=\"large\">瓏門一直係好有創造力既黃店 佢一早表態 又帶頭收美金、各種優惠活動、捐款  </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8JXXqj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8JXXqj.png&h=16201e1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efvLmRZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefvLmRZ.png&h=2535fe03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">當然唔同界別都有唔同努力緊既手足 我廢是太長氣就唔一一舉例 大家一齊發掘</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">故此，杜汶澤呢個係黃圈深受歡迎咁有潛力既企業而家要擴展 發展一個新既平台 對抗藍資紅資企業既壟斷打壓 呢個理由已經夠香港人撐佢 </span><br />\n利申 免費打手 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dj48jGx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDj48jGx.png&h=c29faf24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">黃營企業 自己撐起</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">壯大、對抗、取代、消滅</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f04dd3a8ab5c92